text: Category 6 or Category VI may refer to: * Category 6: Day of Destruction, a 2004 made-for-TV movie * Category 6 cable, a type of cable used for computer networking * A proposed hurricane level above Category 5, on the Saffir- Simpson Hurricane Scale * Category VI protected area (IUCN), with sustainable use of natural resources * Category 6 (album), an album by DJ Laz
title: Category 6
